title: Asset Listing: Add $PAX on ETH v1
body:
Asset Listing: Add $PAX on ETH v1

Intro: This is a vote to list $PAX on ETH v1 with a collateral factor and collateral cap.

Proposal: Via Listing Committee

Rationale: List $PAX on ETH v1 market with collateral factor of 75% and collateral cap of $3M. C.R.E.A.M. will be the first money market to list PAX.

For: 
List $PAX on ETH v1 market with Collateral Factor: 75% and Collateral Cap: $3M.

Against:
Do nothing.
author: 0xd662fA474C0A1346a26374bb4581D1F6D3Fb2d94
